posts.body: These seeded so quickly (up to 20 peers, checked within a hour or two after upload), I wonder if this board is secretly very popular. The same content seems to not be available from another source. So if you post even these exact files somewhere else and they'll be seeded there they won't be found if you try to download them here.

>>43c06203-4f73-4536-8735-0309d08f15ea
That's totally true, I myself got here following a sample link to Zeronet somewhere in a thread about her photoset. I already tried ZN years ago but didn't like its lack of true anonymity. Now that it supports Tor I think it has a future and it's even kinda better that it's not truly anonymous by default. Attracts less criminals and other shady people that stain the software with bad reputation.
Thanks! Some of these look cropped, their filenames suggest much bigger size... I checked another source I found and they're also like that there.

>>880f0e11-9b05-40e3-8cf2-66eba9b7d443
Totally! Just looks a bit weird like they've photobombed that poor poster lol.

>>f51d067b-a14e-442d-948a-11b3d3eaaaf2
Very nice, thanks! I suspected this set is incomplete but that was all I got before the archive was nuked. I downloaded it in full just days before that.

Also, can you please change the subject in your post so it doesn't include asterisks? Looks like it's the reason Millchan can't create a zip with all files.

(thanks, now downloading worked just fine!)
Excellent, thank you! Yeah, this is probably not a full set, let's hope even more pictures get leaked!
